go_data.justification: The TIM22 complex is responsible for importing the large number of metabolite carriers into the inner membrane.
The TIM22 complex inserts the precursors of TIMM23 and TIMM17A/B into the inner membrane.

go_data.term: protein insertion into mitochondrial inner membrane
go_data.justification: TIMM22 also inserts the precursors of TIMM23 and TIMM17A/B into the inner membrane.
